<abstract><t>The device flow is suitable for OAuth 2.0 clients executing on devices that do not have an easy data-entry method (e.g., game consoles, TVs, picture frames, and media hubs), but where the end- user has separate access to a user-agent on another computer or device (e.g., desktop computer, a laptop, a smart phone, or a tablet).</t></abstract>

